- Translation updates: Albanian, Arabic, Asturian, Basque, Bulgarian, Catalan,
  Chinese (China), Chinese (Taiwan), Croatian, Czech, Danish, Dutch,
  English (Australia), English (United Kingdom), Finnish, French, Galician,
